  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Forklift License/Manufacturing, East Region)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, store, and issue goods.</li><li>Operate MHE (forklift, reach truck, pallet jack stacker, VNA).</li><li>Perform stock counts and SAP/EWM transactions.</li><li>Coordinate with team members to improve efficiency.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Valid forklift licence.</li><li>At least 3 years of relevant experience.</li><li>SAP knowledge preferred.</li></ul><p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p><p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p><p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p><p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p><p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
